d'utilisation</span></small><small> </small><small
 style="font-family: arial;"><img src="../images/dbbeusecase.gif"
 title="" alt="" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></small><small>
dans la<span style="font-weight: bold;"> barre d'outils &eacute;dition</span>
.</small></li>
</ul>
<ul style="font-family: arial;">
  <li><small>Avec l'outil </small><small style="font-family: arial;"><span
 style="font-weight: bold;">cas d'utilisation</span></small><small>,
cliquez &agrave; l'int&eacute;rieur de a fen&ecirc;tre du diagramme.</small></li>
</ul>
<small style="font-family: arial;"><font style="font-family: arial;"><font
 color="#000000">.<br>
<br>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">Ajouter un objet </span></font></font><small><span
